e fee constitutes agreement to and acceptance of these terms and conditions. Any form of payment is an acceptance of these terms and conditions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>CHANGES TO THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I reserve the right to add, delete, or modify any provision of these terms and conditions at any time without notice. Failure to receive notification of a change does not make those changes invalid. These terms and conditions will always be available online.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Terms & Conditions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '469-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-23 14:09:55', '2020-06-23 11:09:55', '', 469, 'http://don-dev.thespecialsomething.com/469-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
