e myself, its employees and or agents from all and any liability from:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Loss or damage caused by any inaccuracy;</li><li>Loss or damage caused by omission;</li><li>Loss or damage caused by delay or error, whether the result of negligence or other cause in the production of the project;</li><li>Loss or damage to Clients\' artwork/photos, supplied for the site. Immaterial whether the loss or damage results from negligence or otherwise.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My entire liability to the Client in respect of any claim whatsoever or breach of this agreement, whether or not arising out of negligence, shall be limited to the charges paid for the services under this agreement in respect of which the breach has arisen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>DOMAIN NAMES AND HOSTING</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I may purchase domain names on behalf of the Client. Payment and renewal of those domain names is the responsibility of the Client. The loss, cancellation or otherwise of the domain brought about by non or late payment is not my responsibility. The Client should keep a record of the due dates for payment to ensure that payment is received in good time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With the exception when SEO services are provided, I do not take any responsibility for a Client\'s website rank in search engines. This also includes any potential website downtime that can occur. When updating, changing, creating and hosting a Client\'s website, there could be a change in the website\'s search engine ranking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>GENERAL</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These terms and conditions supersede all previous representations, understandings, or agreements. The Client\'s signature, verbal agreement or payment of an advance fee constitutes agreement to and acceptance of these terms and conditions. Any form of payment is an acceptance of these terms and conditions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>CHANGES TO THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I reserve the right to add, delete, or modify any provision of these terms and conditions at any time without notice. Failure to receive notification of a change does not make those changes invalid. These terms and conditions will always be available online.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Terms & Conditions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '469-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-06-23 14:49:24', '2020-06-23 11:49:24', '', 469, 'http://don-dev.thespecialsomething.com/469-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
